VFIDE_TIER1_PLAN.md:15:- **Diff function bodies before recommending deletion.** Function-name overlap is NOT sufficient evidence of functional equivalence. Before recommending any contract be deleted, diff the actual function bodies and parameter signatures. Added 2026-05-15 after the EscrowManager near-miss where two contracts with overlapping function names had meaningfully different surfaces.
