VFIDE_TIER3_PLAN.md:195:| `app/sanctum/components/CharitiesTab.tsx` | In-tab card grid skeleton |
VFIDE_TIER3_PLAN.md:247:- Guardian forms with `md:col-span-2` grid spanning
VFIDE_TIER3_PLAN.md:323:Section spacing standardized to `py-20` rhythm (was a chaotic mix of `pt-28 pb-20`, `py-10`, `py-14`, `py-16`, `py-20`). Added subtitle to the "Get started in 60 seconds" section to match the "How it works" pattern. Normalized stat strip grid from `gap-8` to `gap-6` for consistency.
VFIDE_TIER3_PLAN.md:357:**Method:** Python regex sweep that targeted the invalid values across `bg-`, `border-`, `text-`, `ring-`, `from-`, `to-`, `via-`, `fill-`, `stroke-` utility prefixes. Conservative: only matched when the invalid value was a complete token (not a substring of a valid number like `/80`).
VFIDE_TIER3_PLAN.md:426:- 80 invalid opacities across other utility prefixes (`/8`, `/6`, `/4`, `/2`, `/12`, `/1`)
VFIDE_TIER3_PLAN.md:467:- **Loading state was just a centered spinner** in an empty container. Replaced with a proper Skeleton grid (8 product card placeholders) that previews the actual layout.
