docs/security/AUDIT_FINDINGS_RUNNING_TODO.md:290:- BATCH-G/#408 — DONE_VALIDATED — LOW/INFO: no event on proposal expiry; off-chain consumers track via `createdAt + PROPOSAL_EXPIRY`; emit on expiry would require explicit invalidation call — accepted as design.
